column5: Heard this afternoon the fishing part of the even has been cancelled due to the lack of QUALITY ice. The event will be a draw prize event.
so  I have a chance of winning then
so  I have a chance of winning then  And one that knows you,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,THATS SOME FUNNY filtered try again please, RIGHT THERE.
It's on their web site:   Im sure it had nothing to do with the fire marshall. It had to do with only having 3-5 inches of ice and over 500+ holes augered. INSURANCE.  Thanks for the post Costa.

Good call spent many tournaments at the sscc, man they made a pretty good breakfast inside, they almost had a draw one year when I was still there, I remember some of the group sponsering the event would meet us out on the ice to sell us tickets ,,,during its infancy, used too think upon their approach that they were co,s in disguise lol
Almost bought a ticket this year a few weeks ago...then I looked at forecast. Maybe I will come up next year. Came in 48th place the first year I entered...nearly won the boat!
My first year was when Chris King held it. Full contact fishing. I won a chain saw for a 1.3 perch. 1st fish brought in.LOL
